tts.qualityDescription: Ikhwalithi ephezulu ikhiqiza umsindo ongcono kodwa isebenzisa i-bandwidth eningi

createDiagrams.title: Dala Amadayagramu
createDiagrams.prompt: Ngikhombise indlela ongadala ngayo amadayagramu namaflowchathi. Yiziphi izinhlobo zezinqubo, imisebenzi, noma izinhlelo ongangisize ngikubone? Nginike izibonelo.

draftContent.title: Bhala Okuqukethwe Kobuchwepheshe
draftContent.prompt: Ngidinga usizo lokubhala amadokhumenti obuchwepheshe - ama-imeyili, imibiko, izifingqo. Ungangibonisa izibonelo zendlela ongasiza ngayo nezinhlobo ezihlukene zokubhala kwebhizinisi?

analyzeInformation.title: Hlaziya Ulwazi
analyzeInformation.prompt: Ungangisiza kanjani ukuhlaziya idatha noma ulwazi? Ngikhombise izindlela ezihlukene ongahlukanisa ngayo izinombolo, uthole amaphethini, noma ukhiphe ulwazi kumadokhumenti noma amaseti edatha.

planOrganize.title: Hlela & Lungisa
planOrganize.prompt: Ungangisiza ukuhlela amaphrojekthi noma ukulungisa umsebenzi? Nginike izibonelo zendlela ongadala ngayo izikali zesikhathi, izinhlelo zomhlangano, noma izinhlelo zamaphrojekthi ezinamasakhiwo ahlukahlukene.

brainstormIdeas.title: Cabanga Amasu
brainstormIdeas.prompt: Ngifuna ukucabanga izixazululo zenkinga. Ngikhombise indlela osondela ngayo ekucabangeni okwakhayo nasekukhiqizeni imicabango - yiziphi izinhlobo zemibuzo ongabuza futhi ucwaninge kanjani amathuba?

buildPresentations.title: Yakha Izethulo
buildPresentations.prompt: Ungangisiza kanjani ukudala izethulo? Ngikhombise izibonelo zamasakhiwo ahlukahlukene ezethulo, iziphakamiso zokubonakala, nendlela ohlela ngayo ulwazi lwabahlukene abalalele.

workWithCode.title: Sebenza Nekhodi
workWithCode.prompt: Ungasiza ngokukhoda noma amaskripti? Ngikhombise izibonelo - noma ngabe ukubhala ikhodi entsha, ukulungisa izinkinga, noma ukuchaza indlela okuthile okusebenza ngayo isinyathelo ngesinyathelo.

decisionSupport.title: Ukusekela Isinqumo
decisionSupport.prompt: Ngidinga ukuthatha isinqumo kodwa angiqiniseki ukuthi ngizihlola kanjani izinketho zami. Ungangibonisa izinhlaka noma izindlela ezihlukene ozisebenzisayo ukusiza ukucabanga ngezinketho?

summarizeSynthesize.title: Fingqa & Hlanganisa
summarizeSynthesize.prompt: Usiza kanjani ngokufingqa amadokhumenti amade noma ukuhlanganisa ulwazi oluvela emithonjeni eminingi? Ngikhombise izibonelo zamafomethi ahlukahlukene okufingqa namazinga emininingwane.

explainTopics.title: Chaza Izihloko Ezinzima
explainTopics.prompt: Ungachaza imiqondo enzima ngamagama alula? Ngikhombise indlela ohlukanisa ngayo imibono enzima, usebenzise izifanekiso, futhi ulungise izincazelo zamazinga ahlukahlukene olwazi.

createSchedules.title: Dala Izinhlelo Zesikhathi
createSchedules.prompt: Ngidinga usizo lokuhlelwa kwesikhathi nokudala izinhlelo zesikhathi. Ngikhombise izindlela ezihlukene ongahlela ngayo izinhlelo zomhlangano, amakhalenda, noma izinhlelo ezisekelwe esikhathini ngezibonelo.

agents.description: Dala futhi uphathe ama-ejensi e-AI angokwezifiso anamakhono akhethekile. Lawa ma-ejensi asebenza ku-MSF AI Assistant Foundry instance.
agents.advancedFeatureTitle: Isici Esithuthukile - Kudinga Ukuxhumana Neqembu Lobuchwepheshe Le-AI Assistant
agents.advancedFeatureWarning: Ama-ejensi angokwezifiso asebenza kuphela ne-MSF AI Assistant Foundry instance. Ama-ID we-ejensi kumele adalwe yiqembu lobuchwepheshe le-AI Assistant kule instance ethile futhi kuxoxiswane nawe ngaphambi kokusebenzisa.
agents.noAgentsDescription: Dala i-ejensi yakho yokuqala yangokwezifiso ukwandisa amakhono e-AI ngamathuluzi nezenzo ezikhethekile.

advancedOptions.title: Izinketho Ezithuthukile
advancedOptions.fixedTemperatureNote: Qaphela: Le modeli isebenzisa amanani angaguquguquki ezinga lokushisa ukuze isebenze ngokuqondile.

searchMode.subtitle: Izosebenzisa ukusesha kwewebhu uma kudingeka

customAgent.description: Le ejensi isebenza ku-MSF AI Assistant Foundry instance namathuluzi avunyelwe njalo.

modelTypeIcons.foundational: Imodeli esheshayo nesebenza kahle yezinjongo ezijwayelekile
modelTypeIcons.agent: I-ejensi enamathuluzi esikhathi sangempela nokufinyelela kwewebhu

gpt_4_1.name: GPT-4.1
gpt_4_1.description: Imodeli ye-AI esebenziswa yi-GPT-4.1 nokusesha kwewebhu kwesikhathi sangempela nge-Bing. Ihlinzeka ngolwazi olusha, ukuhlolwa kwamaqiniso, nokwazi izenzakalo zamanje. Iyinhle kakhulu ocwaningweni oludinga ulwazi olusha, ukuhlaziywa kwezindaba, nokuqinisekiswa kwamaqiniso.

gpt_5_2.name: GPT-5.2
gpt_5_2.description: Imodeli ethuthukile kakhulu ye-OpenAI, ehluke ekucabangeni okuzinzile, ukukhiqiza ikhodi, nokuxazulula izinkinga zobuchwepheshe. Iyinhle kakhulu emisebenzini yokuhlaziya, izinselele zokuhlela, ucwaningo, nezincazelo ezinemininingwane. Isekela umzamo wokucabanga oshintshekayo namazinga emininingwane yempendulo.

gpt_5_mini.name: GPT-5 Mini
gpt_5_mini.description: Inguqulo esheshayo neshibhile ye-GPT-5, elungiselelwe isivinini ngesikhathi igcina ikhwalithi ephezulu. Iphelele emisebenzini yansuku zonke, imibuzo esheshayo, ukuqondiswa kwamathuluzi, nezinhlelo zokusebenza ezidinga isikhathi sempendulo esisheshayo. Ibhalansi enhle yokusebenza kanye nokusebenza kahle.

gpt_5_2_chat.name: GPT-5.2 Ingxoxo
gpt_5_2_chat.description: Inguqulo ekhethekile ye-GPT-5.2 elungiselelwe ukuxoxisana nemizwa. Iyinhle ekuxhumaneni okunozwela, ukusekela kwempilo yengqondo, ukubhala okwakhayo, ukucabanga amasu, nengxoxo yemvelo. Iyinhle kakhulu ezingxoxweni ezejwayelekile, izimo zokululeka, nemisebenzi edinga ukuqonda imizwa.

o3.name: o3
o3.description: Imodeli yokucabanga ethuthukile kakhulu ye-OpenAI enamakhono amasha okuxazulula izinkinga. Iyinhle kakhulu kwezibalo ezinzima, ukucabanga kwesayensi, izinselele zokukhoda, nemisebenzi yezigaba eziningi zomqondo. Iwindi elibonakala ngaphakathi elinezinhlamvu ezingu-200K. Isekela ukulawula umzamo wokucabanga.

llama_4_maverick.name: Llama 4 Maverick
llama_4_maverick.description: Imodeli esheshayo neshibhile evela ku-Meta. Iyinhle emisebenzini yansuku zonke efana nokubhala, ukufingqa, nosizo lokukhoda oluyisisekelo. Ibhalansi enhle yesivinini nekhwalithi yomsebenzi ojwayelekile.

deepseek_r1.name: DeepSeek-R1
deepseek_r1.description: Uchwepheshe wokucabanga okhombisa umsebenzi wakhe isinyathelo ngesinyathelo. Iyinhle kakhulu ezinkingeni zezibalo, amaphazili omqondo, nokuqonda imiqondo enzima. Bona indlela ecabanga ngayo izinkinga ngesikhathi sangempela.

deepseek_v3_1.name: DeepSeek-V3.1
deepseek_v3_1.description: Imodeli eqinile yonke indawo ikakhulukazi enhle ekukhodeni nasekubhaleni kwezobuchwepheshe. Iyinhle ekulungiseni ikhodi, ekubhaleni amadokhumenti, nasekuchazeni imiqondo yezobuchwepheshe. Iyashesha futhi ithembekile emsebenzini wokuthuthukisa.

grok_3.name: Grok 3
grok_3.description: Imodeli ehlukahlukene evela ku-xAI eyaziwa ngezimpendulo ezijulile. Iyinhle ezingxoxweni ezivulekile, amaphrojekthi okudala, nokukhela izinkinga ezinzima.

claude_opus_4_5.name: Claude Opus 4.5
claude_opus_4_5.description: Imodeli enamandla kakhulu ye-Anthropic enamakhono okucabanga, ukukhoda, nokudala okumangalisayo. Iyinhle kakhulu ekuhlaziyeni okuzinzile, ucwaningweni, nemisebenzi edinga ukuqonda okujulile.

claude_sonnet_4_5.name: Claude Sonnet 4.5
claude_sonnet_4_5.description: Imodeli ye-Claude elinganisiwe ehlinzeka ngokusebenza okuhle kakhulu ekukhodeni, ekuhlaziyeni, nasemisebenzini yokudala. Iyinhle ekusetshenzisweni kwansuku zonke nesikhathi sempendulo esisheshayo.

claude_opus_4_1.name: Claude Opus 4.1
claude_opus_4_1.description: Imodeli ye-Claude Opus yesizukulwane esedlule. Iyinhle kakhulu emisebenzini yokukhoda enzima, ukuhlaziywa okumininingwane, nokuqonda okujulile.

claude_haiku_4_5.name: Claude Haiku 4.5
claude_haiku_4_5.description: Imodeli ye-Claude esheshayo neshibhile elungiselelwe imisebenzi esheshayo. Iyinhle emibutweni elula, ukufingqa, nezinhlelo zokusebenza ezinenani eliphezulu.

searchMode.subtitle: Ukuqonda izinketho zakho zokusesha nendawo lapho idatha yakho igcinwa khona
searchMode.noSearchDescription: Izimpendulo ezisheshe kakhulu ngaphandle kwamandla okusesha kwewebhu. Ingxoxo yakho yonke ihlala esipheqululini sakho - akukho okugcinwa efwini.
searchMode.viewDetailsBelow: Ukuthola imininingwane eyengeziwe, buka umsebenzi wobuchwepheshe ngezansi.
searchMode.legendNoSearch: Isiphequluli Sakho (isitoreji sendawo) | Iseva ye-AI Assistant | Azure OpenAI (akunasimo)
searchMode.privacyDescription: Isebenzisa ukusesha kwewebhu uma kudingeka kodwa ikuncane ngoba kunezinyathelo eziningi. Imibuzo yokusesha kuphela egcinwa ku-Azure - ingxoxo yakho yonke ihlala esipheqululini sakho.
searchMode.legendPrivacy: Isiphequluli Sakho (isitoreji sendawo) | Iseva ye-AI Assistant | Azure AI Foundry (imibuzo yokusesha kuphela) | Azure OpenAI (akunasimo)
searchMode.foundryDescription: Izimpendulo ezisheshayo namakhono okusesha kwewebhu afakiwe. Ingxoxo yakho yonke igcinwa ku-database ye-Azure AI Foundry, hhayi esipheqululini sakho kuphela.
searchMode.legendFoundry: Isiphequluli Sakho (isitoreji sendawo) | Iseva ye-AI Assistant | I-ejensi ye-Azure AI Foundry (igcina ingxoxo ephelele)
searchMode.whyTheseOptionsText1: Lezi yizinqubo zokusesha ezitholakalayo ngemva kokuthi i-Azure isuse i-Bing Search API yayo, leyo i-AI Assistant eyayithembele kuyo ekuqaleni.
searchMode.whyTheseOptionsText2: Iqembu lihlola ngokusebenzayo izindlela zokusesha ezigxile kakhulu ebumfihlweni. Zombili izinketho zamanje zisebenzisa amakhono okusesha e-Azure AI Foundry kodwa zihlukile ekuthini idatha yengxoxo engakanani ibiwa.
searchMode.azureDeprecatedBingApi: I-Azure isuse i-Bing Search API yayo
searchMode.footerNote: Zombili imimodi igcina ingxoxo yakho endaweni esipheqululini sakho. Ungashintsha imimodi noma nini kuzilungiselelo zemodeli.

dropdown.searchTooltip:
Vumela ukusesha kwewebhu kuwo wonke umlayezo.

Kunikeza ulwazi olusha kusetshenziswa ukufinyelela kwe-Bing kwewebhu ngqo.
dropdown.attachTooltip:
Namathisela amafayela, izithombe, noma omsindo/ividiyo.

Amafomathi asekelwayo:
‚Ä¢ Izithombe: JPEG, PNG, GIF, WebP (5MB max, kuze kube-10)
‚Ä¢ Amadokhumenti: PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX, TXT, MD (10MB max, kuze kube-3)
‚Ä¢ Idatha: CSV, JSON, XML, YAML (10MB max, kuze kube-3)
‚Ä¢ Ikhodi: PY, JS, TS, JAVA, C, CPP, GO, njll. (10MB max, kuze kube-3)
‚Ä¢ Omsindo/Ividiyo: MP3, WAV, MP4, WebM (25MB max, ifayela eli-1)

Isamba: amafayela angu-10, 50MB max
dropdown.transcribeTooltip:
Layisha amafayela omsindo noma evidiyo ukuze abhalwe phansi.

Amafomathi asekelwayo: MP3, MP4, WAV, WebM, M4A, MPEG, MPGA
Ubukhulu obukhulu: 25MB

Ukubhalwa phansi kwenzeka ngokuzenzakalela uma uthumela umlayezo.
dropdown.translateDocumentTooltip:
Humusha amadokhumenti kolunye ulimi.

Amafomathi asekelwayo: Word, Excel, PowerPoint, PDF, HTML, TXT
Ubukhulu obukhulu: 40MB

Kusekela izilimi ezingu-80+ namafayela ezichazamazwi angakhethwa.
